query:
SELECT id, userId, status, totalRows, processedRows, 
       DATE_FORMAT(createdAt, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') as created,
       DATE_FORMAT(startedAt, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') as started,
       errorMessage
FROM crmMergeJobs 
ORDER BY createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 10;
